  <releases>
    <release version="2.0" date="2022-04-22">
      <description>
        <p>Flowtime 2.0: Keep on track!</p>
        <p>In this new version, a shiny new feature was added: Statistics!</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Have an overview of how much time you have worked in the last month, week and day</li>
          <li>Take a look at your day-specific data</li>
          <li>Export your statistics to CSV format</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="1.5.0" date="2022-03-12">
      <description>
        <p>Version 1.5.0</p>
        <p>After a long time of this version finally has arrived with small, yet new features!</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Accent color changes depending on your stage: blue for work stage, green for break stage</li>
          <li>There is now a label above the timer that indicates your current stage</li>
          <li>A new setting has arrived: Timer Autostart. Set if you want to start the timer inmediately after you press the "next" button</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
  </releases>

